# Personal Dashboard (Project 2)

## Stack
- Next.js App Router, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS
- Data: browser `localStorage` via `src/lib/storage.ts` (SSR-safe helpers — no `localStorage` at module scope in Server Components)

## Product context
- Read `prd_project2_dashboard.md` for workshop scope and stretch goals
- Read `README.md` for onboarding, build order, and suggested Cursor prompts (participants decide what they track there or in chat)

## Build order (suggested)
1. Extend the data model in `src/lib/sample-data.ts` to match what the user is tracking (see README)
2. Add form → persist with `saveItems` / `loadItems` from Client Components or `useEffect`
3. List/grid → then filters or status toggles
4. Add `"use client"` only where you need browser APIs, state, or events

## Conventions
- Shared types: `DashboardItem` in `src/lib/sample-data.ts`
- Reusable UI: `src/components/`
- App routes and layouts: `src/app/`
